# GitHub Open Source
Host github.com
    User git
    Hostname github.com
    IdentityFile ~/.ssh/github-personal.pub
    IdentitiesOnly yes

# GitHub Enterprise Cloud
Host github-zse
    User git
    Hostname github.com
    IdentityFile ~/.ssh/github-zse.pub
    IdentitiesOnly yes

Host *
  IdentityAgent "~/.1password/agent.sock"
